Third-Party Software Notices

PQ Journal depends on third-party packages installed separately by the user.
This software does not bundle or redistribute those packages. Each carries its
own license terms, which users accept upon installation.

Core dependencies (MIT / BSD / Apache 2.0 — all permissive open source):
  fastapi, uvicorn, starlette     MIT / BSD
  jinja2, itsdangerous            BSD
  sqlalchemy, aiosqlite           MIT
  cryptography                    Apache 2.0 / BSD
  liboqs-python                   MIT  (Open Quantum Safe project)
  pydantic-settings, pyyaml       MIT
  numpy, psutil, httpx            BSD

Optional AI dependencies (MIT / BSD / Apache 2.0):
  faster-whisper                  MIT
  vosk                            Apache 2.0
  transformers                    Apache 2.0  (Hugging Face)
  torch (PyTorch)                 BSD-3-Clause
  deepface                        MIT
