  weasyprint                      BSD

AI model weights (downloaded separately on first use):
  OpenAI Whisper model weights    MIT
  j-hartmann/emotion-english-*   Apache 2.0
  DeepFace emotion weights        MIT

Ollama and language model weights:
  Ollama                          MIT  (https://github.com/ollama/ollama)
  Llama 3.2 model weights         Meta Llama 3 Community License
